vajramudraṇīyatvena mudrātvametāsāṃ mokṣahetutayā pratipādyata ityarthaḥ | vajramudrāḥ satyaḥ sarvāvaraṇavimokṣalakṣaṇaṃ mokṣamāvahantīti yāvat |

<commentary>pañcakulāni na jñāyanta iti tānyāha | pañcakulalakṣaṇānupalakṣaṇasādhāraṇaṃ kulamapekṣyāha—uttamānīti |</commentary>

eṣāṃ kulānāmuttamatve kimetāsāmityāha—vajramityādi |
